  "title": "Senior Cook – Karnataka / Bangalore Bar Cuisine",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are an Indian bar specialising in authentic Karnataka (Bangalore-style) bar bites and small plates. We are looking for an experienced Senior Cook with strong hands-on knowledge of Bangalore food culture, traditional flavours, and popular bar snacks commonly served in Karnataka.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare regional Karnataka dishes accurately to maintain authenticity and meet menu standards</li><li>Apply knowledge of Karnataka spice blends and masalas to create traditional flavours consistently</li><li>Cook Bangalore-style bar snacks efficiently to maintain speed and quality during peak service hours</li><li>Manage kitchen operations to ensure smooth food preparation and timely delivery</li><li>Maintain kitchen hygiene and food safety standards to comply with health regulations</li><li>Work independently with minimal supervision to complete assigned cooking tasks</li><li>Collaborate with team members to support kitchen workflow and uphold a positive work environment</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 5 years of relevant cooking experience, with strong exposure to Karnataka / Bangalore cuisine</li><li>Hands-on experience cooking Bangalore-style food (not just general Indian cuisine)</li><li>Familiarity with Bangalore food culture, street food, and bar-style dishes</li><li>Ability to work efficiently during peak service hours</li><li>Team player with a positive attitude and strong work ethic</li></ul>",
